entry.title: Russia Says Ukrainian Commandos Stage Cross-Border Incursion
entry.content: Russia said that its military and security forces were moving to eliminate Ukrainian commandos who had crossed the border, a rare incursion that appeared to catch Moscow off guard.

entry.title: Rising Nuclear-Weapons Risks Overshadow G-7's Push for Disarmament at Hiroshima
